title: Racing A NASCAR over 130 MPH
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
itunes:summary:
In this podcast we have our friend Nick Antonyan join us, we chat about our day driving NASCARs on a track, the new bus stop bench advertisements we bought to advertise our podcast, Nick being a super fan of our podcast, and catching two people making love near our bench. Plus we give away $225 to a listener of our podcast!


Make sure to follow our instagram @lightweightspod
